{"tid":325852,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"日本psv銷量居然仲高過ps4?","createTime":"2017-07-17T13:28:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T01:28:54.000Z","uid":80323,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f5ec32d80c4f7fc3a4e7039d7c24cb206a55eceb","tid":325852,"uid":80323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T13:28:52.000Z","msg":"截至17年上半年，日本ps4總銷量係4,799,246，而psv就係5,507,715，xbox one就少到得78,041<br />\n<a href=\"http://sina.com.hk/news/article/20170706/0/5/2/2017%E5%B9%B4%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%BB%E6%A9%9F%E5%92%8C%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E9%8A%B7%E9%87%8F%E5%85%AC%E4%BD%88-7647164.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20170706%2F0%2F5%2F2%2F2017%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%2592%258C%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%2588%25B2%25E9%258A%25B7%25E9%2587%258F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E4%25BD%2588-7647164.html&d=OB4OchlGuQADUX0z5a5s3jQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=539af97c\" target=\"_blank\">http://sina.com.hk/news/article/20170706/0/5/2/2017%E5%B9%B4%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%BB%E6%A9%9F%E5%92%8C%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E9%8A%B7%E9%87%8F%E5%85%AC%E4%BD%88-7647164.html</a><br />\n<br />\nps4全球銷量係6040萬，psv銷量係一千五百幾萬(VGchartz數據)，xbox one以前就有人估計過係ps4既一半。<br />\n明明ps4銷量大約係psv既4倍，但係日本竟然可以調返轉，psv銷量仲高過ps4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac67472fb6ce81542a39663381714e5789524209","tid":325852,"uid":14065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T15:24:31.000Z","msg":"PSV多毒撚GAME"},{"pid":"b0d1527e5f09676f081f6b2727ae9427b2e240fa","tid":325852,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T19:35:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>PSV多毒撚GAME</blockquote><br />\n紳士game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日本係興手提機多過家用機"},{"pid":"cb9bd2b095070e14c60060757366